<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Email Verification - Prof Bioresearch</title>
</head>

<body
    style="margin:0; padding:0; background-color:#f4f6f9; color:#333; font-family:'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; -moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;">

    <div
        style="max-width:600px; margin:30px auto; background-color:#ffffff; border-radius:10px; overflow:hidden; box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div style="background-color:#0056b3; color:#ffffff; padding:20px 30px; text-align:center;">
            <h1 style="margin:0; font-size:24px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.5px;">
                Verify Your Email
            </h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div style="padding:30px; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6; color:#444;">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>Prof Bioresearch</strong>. To complete the setup of your employee account, please
                verify your email address using the code below:</p>

            <div
                style="text-align:center; font-size:28px; font-weight:bold; color:#0056b3; margin:30px 0; letter-spacing:2px;">
                {{code}}
            </div>

            <p>Enter this code on the verification page to confirm your email address. For security reasons, this code
                will expire in <strong>30 minutes</strong>.</p>

            <p>If you did not initiate this process, please disregard this message.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br /><strong>The Prof Bioresearch Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div style="text-align:center; padding:20px; font-size:13px; color:#777; background-color:#f1f1f1;">
            &copy; {{year}} Prof Bioresearch Â· All rights reserved<br />
            <a href="https://www.profbioresearch.com"
                style="color:#0056b3; text-decoration:none;">www.profbioresearch.com</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>